::GoldenEye::

She was flying when she saw the pod fall to the ground like a falling 
star.  She swooped down and perched on a branch to see what would 
come out of the pod.  Nothing came out so she flew down and landed 
next to the pod.  She transformed into bot mode and looked at the 
pod.  She knocked on the top of it. "Hello, Any body in there?"

She stood back to see if something inside would come out. She just 
hoped it was Predacon, what ever it was.
